 diagonal HD screen into a smaller footprint. And the HP Wide Vision HD camera makes you look good too.<br /><br />LEAN IN. THEN LEAN BACK.: Power through your to-do list and power up your play list with a long battery life, ample storage and an Intel® processor.<br /><br />KEEP IT ALL IN SYNC: Everything is connected. Chrome OS syncs your life for a simple and secure digital experience. And your favorite Android apps are here too.<br /><br />CHROME: This easy-to-use operating system was designed to be fast in every possible way, while keeping you safe and more secure on the web.<br /><br />DUAL-CORE INTEL® CELERON® PROCESSOR: The HP Chromebook perfectly combines performance, power consumption, and value to help your day run smoothly and reliably with two processing cores to handle all your tasks.<br /><br />INTEL® UHD GRAPHICS: Smoothly stream 4K content and play your favorite games on your Chromebook x360.<br /><br />HD TOUCHSCREEN: Pinch, zoom, and swipe to intuitively control your HP Chromebook x360 laptop right from the screen.<br /><br />HP FAST CHARGE: When this long battery life laptop needs charging, it can go from 0 to 50% charge in approximately 45 minutes.<br /><br />64 GB EMMC STORAGE: An embedded multimedia card provides reliable flash-based storage for this HP Chromebook 14.<br /><br />WI-FI 5 AND BLUETOOTH® 5.0: With a Wi-Fi 5 adapter and Bluetooth® 5.0, all your connections are rock solid.<br /><br />DDR4 RAM: With higher bandwidth, give your dual-core laptop more of a boost in performance.<br /><br />360º GEARED HINGE: Innovatively engineered to rotate 360 degrees so that you can use your HP 14.0 Chromebook in four positions.<br /><br />GOOGLE ASSISTANT: Work faster and smarter with Google Assistant. Seamlessly multitask, ask questions and control your Chromebook entertainment - all hands-free with a simple voice command.<br /><br />HDMI COMPATIBILITY: Connect to devices with HDMI using a USB-C to HDMI Adapter (adapter sold separately).<br /><br />