mary_barcode"=>"195122198749", "product_classification"=>{"product_type_name"=>"ELECTRONICS"}, "product_description"=>{"title"=>"HP 14&#34; Convertible 2-in-1 Chromebook Laptop with Chrome OS - Intel Processor - 4GB RAM Memory - 64GB Flash Storage - Mineral Silver (14a-ca0036nr)", "downstream_description"=>"A view that adjusts to you. The HP Chromebook 14a convertible laptop has a commanding view of entertainment at any angle and the power to tackle work and play all day. With a 13-hour battery life, the familiarity of Chrome OS plus all your favorite Android apps, your digital life is completely organized.<br /><br />FLEXIBILITY LOOKS GOOD ON YOU: Watch anyway you want. The slim, supremely flexible design of this silver Chromebook packs a 14-inch diagonal HD screen into a smaller footprint. And the HP Wide Vision HD camera makes you look good too.<br /><br />LEAN IN. THEN LEAN BACK.: Power through your to-do list and power up your play list with a long battery life, ample storage and an Intel® processor.<br /><br />KEEP IT ALL IN SYNC: Everything is connected. Chrome OS syncs your life for a simple and secure digital experience. And your favorite Android apps are here too.<br /><br />CHROME: This easy-to-use operating system was designed to be fast in every possible way, while keeping you safe and more secure on the web.<br /><br />DUAL-CORE INTEL® CELERON® PROCESSOR: The HP Chromebook perfectly combines performance, power consumption, and value to help your day run smoothly and reliably with two processing cores to handle all your tasks.<br /><br />INTEL® UHD GRAPHICS: Smoothly stream 4K content and play your favorite games on your Chromebook x360.<br /><br />HD TOUCHSCREEN: Pinch, zoom, and swipe to intuitively control your HP Chromebook x360 laptop right from the screen.<br /><br />HP FAST CHARGE: When this long battery life laptop needs charging, it can go from 0 to 50% charge in approximately 45 minutes.<br /><br />64 GB EMMC STORAGE: An embedded multimedia card provides reliable flash-based storage for this HP Chromebook 14.<br /><br />WI-FI 5 AND BLUETOOTH® 5.0: With a Wi-Fi 5 adapter and Bluetooth® 5.0, all your connections are rock solid.<br /><br />DDR4 RAM: With higher bandwidth, give your dual-core laptop more of a boost in performance.<br /><br />360º GEARED HINGE: Innovatively engineered to rotate 360 degrees so that you can use your HP 14.0 Chromebook in four positions.<br /><br />GOOGLE ASSISTANT: Work faster and smarter with Google Assistant. Seamlessly multitask, ask questions and control your Chromebook entertainment - all hands-free with a simple voice command.<br /><br />HDMI COMPATIBILITY: Connect to devices with HDMI using a USB-C to HDMI Adapter (adapter sold separately).<br /><br />Additional features: HP Wide Vision 720p HD camera with integrated dual array digital microphone, full-size keyboard, HD Audio with stereo speakers, 1-year limited hardware warranty", "bullet_descriptions"=>["<B>Dimensions (Overall):</B> .72 Inches (H) x 12.81 Inches (W) x 8.65 Inches (D)", "<B>Weight:</B> 3.3 Pounds", "<B>Hard Drive Speed:</B> No Rotation", "<B>Battery Charge Life:</B> Up to 13 Hours", "<B>Electronics Condition:</B> New", "<B>Number of USB ports:</B> 3", "<B>Electronics Features:</B> Microsoft 365 Compatible, High Definition Audio, Multi-Touch Gesture Support, Built-In Bluetooth, High Definition Display, Built-In Speaker, Built-In Webcam, Dual Speakers, Video Conferencing Capable", "<B>Processor Type:</B> Intel Celeron", "<B>Aspect Ratio:</B> 16:9 Aspect Ratio", "<B>Operating System:</B> Google Chrome OS", "<B>Data Storage Drive Capacity:</B> 64GB eMMC", "<B>Includes:</B> Power cord", "<B>Screen Resolution:</B> 1366 x 768", "<B>Connection Types:</B> MicroSD, USB, USB-C", "<B>Video Recording Resolution:</B> 720p", "<B>Native screen refresh rate:</B> 60 Hz", "<B>Wireless Technology:</B> Wi-Fi 5 (IEEE 802.11ac), Bluetooth 5.0", "<B>Screen Size:</B> 14 Inches", "<B>Drive Type:</B> No Drive", "<B>Processor Spee