ays secure and up to date, and access to a huge selection of apps in the Google Play Store.<br /><br />CHROME OS: This easy-to-use operating system was designed to be fast in every possible way, while keeping you safe and more secure on the web.<br /><br />PLUS CHROMEBOOK: Offering fast performance and web browsing, smooth video calls, and ample storage for apps, photos and movies.<br /><br />GOOGLE ASSISTANT VOICE COMMANDS: Work faster and smarter with Google Assistant. Seamlessly multitask, ask questions and control your Chromebook entertainment—all hands-free with a simple voice command.<br /><br />QUAD-CORE INTEL® PENTIUM® SILVER PROCESSOR: Handle multitasking reliably with the perfect combination of performance, power consumption, and value.<br /><br />HP FAST CHARGE: Go from 0 to 50% charge in approximately 45 minutes.<br /><br />HIGH DEFINITION DISPLAY AND TRULY POWERFUL AUDIO: Enjoy your entertainment with the great quality and high-definition detail of 1 million pixels. HP Dual Speakers, custom-tuned by experts at B&O, deliver rich, authentic audio.<br /><br />WI-FI 5 & BLUETOOTH 5.0: With a Wi-Fi 5 (802.11a/b/g/n/ac) WLAN<br />adapter and Bluetooth® 5.0, all your connections are rock solid so you have a great connection to your online class, video chat and whatever else your day has in store. Pair with a MU-MIMO router for a smoother online experience in multi-device homes.<br /><br />HP WIDE VISION HD CAMERA WITH DUAL ARRAY MICROPHONES: 88-degree, wide-angle field of view for video chats. <br /><br />MULTI-TOUCH GESTURES ON THE TOUCHPAD: This true multi-touch touchpad supports four finger gestures and lets you scroll, zoom, and navigate with a simple touch.<br /><br />WARRANTY: 1-year limited hardware warranty. Additional information available at www.support.hp.com. Full warranty details are included with your product. 90 days limited technical support for software and initial setup (from date of purchase).", "bullet_descriptions"=>["<B>Dimensions (Overal