>"https://pubads.g.doubleclick.net/gampad/adx?m=application/json&sz=1x1&iu=/7079046/tgt/5xtg6/5xtfc/5xtf4&t=pt%3Dproductdetails%26nap%3Dand%26item%3D82459042%26cat%3D5xtf4"}}}, {"data"=>{"product"=>{"tcin"=>"80339975", "item"=>{"dpci"=>"056-01-0100", "assigned_selling_channels_code"=>"online_and_stores", "primary_barcode"=>"192876840665", "product_classification"=>{"product_type_name"=>"ELECTRONICS"}, "product_description"=>{"title"=>"Asus 15.6&#34; Chromebook Laptop, 64GB Storage, Full HD Display 1920 x 1080 Resolution, Silver (C523NA-TH44F)", "downstream_description"=>"ASUS Chromebook C523 is the simple way to boost your productivity and have more fun on the move — all day and every day. This ultraportable and lightweight 15.6-inch Chromebook is powered by an Intel® processor, and gives you the freedom of up to 10 hours battery life.<br /><br />Strong, stylish and light<br />With its aluminum-finished lid, thin 15.6mm profile and overall weight of just 3.15 lbs., ASUS Chromebook C523 has a distinctively premium look and feel. <br /><br />Stunning vision<br />The stunning 15.6-inch FHD NanoEdge display has an ultra-narrow 6mm bezel, and features a matte anti-glare coating to reduce reflections. The result is a laptop with an impressive 80% screen-to-body ratio that minimizes size while helping you maximize productivity — so you can see and do more, while carrying less.<br /><br />Durable 180° hinge<br />ASUS Chromebook C523 can be laid flat to share content easily with friends and colleagues. Its unique, durable hinge design has been subjected to a grueling 20,000-cycle open-and-close test to ensure long-term reliability.<br /><br />USB-C for ultimate flexibility<br />Two full-function reversible USB-C™ (Type-C™) ports make it easy to charge ASUS Chromebook C523 or connect it to devices and external displays. USB-C provides superfast data-transfer speeds.  For maximum convenience and compatibility, ASUS Chromebook C523 also features standard USB 3.1 ports, and there's a microSD slot for adding more storage.<br /><br />Faster, more stable Wi-Fi connections<br />ASUS Chromebook C523 includes dual-band 802.11ac Wi-Fi for strong, stable signals and fast data-transmission speeds.  <br /><br />Powerfully clear sound<br />ASUS Chromebook C523 doesn’t compromise on sound quality. With dual high-quality stereo speakers and extra-large resonant chambers that generate high-fidelity audio, it can deliver surround-sound effects, with crisp and powerful sound to give an immersive experience for both music and video streaming.<br /> ", "bullet_descriptions"=>["<B>Dimensions (Overall):</B> .6 Inches (H) x 14.1 Inches (W) x 9.8 Inches (D)", "<B>Weight:</B> 3.1 Pounds", "<B>Hard Drive Speed:</B> No Rotation", "<B>Battery Charge Life:</B> Up to 10 Hours", "<B>Electronics Condition:</B> New", "<B>Number of USB ports:</B> 4", "<B>Electronics Features:</B> Anti-Glare Coating, Backlit Display, Built-In Bluetooth, Voice Control, Touchpad, Built-In Speaker, Built-In Webcam, LED Display", "<B>Processor Type:</B> Intel Celeron", "<B>Aspect Ratio:</B> 16:9 Aspect Ratio", "<B>Operating System:</B> Google Chrome OS", "<B>Data Storage Drive Capacity:</B> 64GB eMMC", "<B>Includes:</B> Battery, AC Power Adapter", "<B>Screen Resolution:</B> 1920 x 1080", "<B>Connection Types:</B> 3.5mm Jack, MicroSD, USB, USB-C", "<B>Video Recording Resolution:</B> 720p", "<B>Wireless Technology:</B> Bluetooth 4.0", "<B>Screen Size:</B> 15.6 Inches", "<B>Drive Type:</B> No Drive", "<B>Processor Speed:</B> 1.1 GHz", "<B>System RAM:</B> 4 GB", "<B>Memory RAM Type:</B> LPDDR4", "<B>RAM Configuration:</B> 1x4GB", "<B>Display Type:</B> TN Panel", "<B>Primary use:</B> Home", "<B>Number of cores:</B> 2", "<B>Data storage type:</B> EMMC", "<B>Graphics card model:</B> Intel HD Graphics 500", "<B>Processor model:</B> N3350", "<B>Touchscreen:</B> No Touchscreen Display", "<B>Data storage capacity:</B> 64 GB", "<B>Microphone:</B> Built-In Microphone", "<B>RAM Slots (Total):</B> 0", "<B>Backlit Keyboard:</B> No Backlit Keyboard", "<B>Warranty:</B> 1 Year Limited Warranty. To obtain a copy of the manufacturer's or supplier's warranty for this item prior to purchasing the item, please call Target Guest Services at 1-800-591-3869"], "soft_bullets"=>{"title"=>"highlights", "bullets"=>["15.6 inch Full HD anti-glare NanoEdge display and 180-degree lay-flat hinge", "Chromebook runs on Chrome OS and has the Google apps where you can edit, download and convert", "Power through the day with an Intel Celeron N3350 Processor", "Explore and store with 4GB LPDDR4 RAM and 64GB eMMC storage", "Portable and long-lasting with up to 10 hours of battery life at only 3.15 lb", "Access to Microsoft Word, Excel®, or Powerpoint® on the web", "Stay connected with Wi-Fi 5, Bluetooth 4.0, 2x USB Type-C ports, 2x USB Type-A, a micro SD card reader, and an HD Camera"]}}, "compliance"=>{"is_proposition_65"=>true, "proposition_65_warning_text"=>"Cancer and Reproductive Harm-WWW.P65Warnings.ca.gov"}, "enrichment"=>{"buy_url"=>"https://www.target.com/p/asus-15-6-34-chromebook-laptop-64gb-storage-full-hd-display-1920-x-1080-resolution-silver-c523na-th44f/-/A-80339975", "images"=>{"primary_image_url"=>"https://target.scene7.com/is/image/Target/GUEST_d6a09ec5-0b63-4ad1-b142-c2bebb183378", "alternate_image_urls"=>["https://target.scene7.com/is/image/Target/GUEST_a91486a4-029e-4a7a-8701-9696934e3717", "https://target.scene7.com/is/image/Target/GUEST_3e18d3c4-7da6-4a18-adf5-f6c1ed2e61a3", "https://target.scene7.com/is/image/Target/GUEST_8812a974-62f8-4dd4-9c74-774c737eeb7a", "https://target.scene7.com/is/image/Target/GUEST_acb94b2d-bbfb-4437-b46f-33de3246d5c9", "https://target.scene7.com/is/image/Target/GUEST_d3bdc0f0-e1a8-46a6-a959-1b79990d583f"], "content_labels"=>[{"image_url"=>"https://target.scene7.com/is/image/Target/GUEST_d3bdc0f0-e1a8-46a6-a959-1b79990d583f"}, {"image_url"=>"https://target.scene7.com/is/image/Target/GUEST_acb94b2d-bbfb-4437-b46f-33de3246d5c9"}, {"image_url"=>"htt